ğŸ¥ YouTube Video Q&A Bot (LLM + LangChain + Gradio)
ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
This project is an AI-powered YouTube assistant that allows users to paste a YouTube video link and ask questions about the video content.
The system automatically:


Extracts the video ID from the URL
Fetches the transcript using YouTube Transcript API
Cleans and preprocesses the text
Splits the transcript into chunks
Generates embeddings and stores them in a FAISS vector database
Performs semantic search to find relevant content
Uses an LLM (OpenAI via LangChain) to generate accurate answers
Provides an interactive UI using Gradio


